{"tid":2216420,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企多過兩個人 冇可能得一個廁所","createTime":"2020-09-24T15:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T10:54:48.000Z","uid":239146,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"55f48bb9dff98b5e684b856f7e07b3ac32bbee8d","tid":2216420,"uid":239146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"我屋企一家三口 有兩個廁所<br />\n但有時都唔夠用 一齊食完早餐會三個一齊急屎<br />\n係屋企都好啲 可以開口互相遷就<br />\n<br />\n我男朋友一家三口 得一個廁所<br />\n我有時過去訓 食完早餐好急屎<br />\n佢老豆就成日霸住個廁所修剪啲花花草草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔好意思叫佢讓我<br />\n又怕痾完好臭 佢入去繼續剪草好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試過我凌晨四點痾夜尿<br />\n佢老豆又痾夜尿 痾夜尿都要等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個屋企多過兩個人 得一個廁所真係會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4666ea4ee344d2eef8c825d563e49975cb8d658","tid":2216420,"uid":320680,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T15:51:28.000Z","msg":"我一家三口有四個厠所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83142579188bee4a0c31beb98ddba20cd00cc351","tid":2216420,"uid":323845,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"a4666ea4ee344d2eef8c825d563e49975cb8d658","tid":2216420,"uid":320680,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T15:51:28.000Z","msg":"我一家三口有四個厠所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T15:52:06.000Z","msg":"你屋企係公廁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866335548dbc5b8068b9ba0a9d67a29b6929c503","tid":2216420,"uid":320680,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,